<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.4">
<l>viḷaitta vempōr viṟalvā ḷarakkaṉ nakarpāḻpaṭa</l>
<l>vaḷaitta valvil taṭakkai yavaṉuk kiṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>tuḷaikkai yāṉai maruppu makiluṅ koṇarntuntimuṉ</l>
<l>tiḷaikkuñ celvap puṉalkā viricūḻ teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place for him with broad hands</l>
<l rend="indent">who bent the strong bow</l>
<l>To raze the city of the demon with the brave sword made for harsh battle,</l>
<l>Is Araṅkam of the South encircled by the Kāviri</l>
<l rend="indent">with bounteous waters which surge</l>
<l>Carrying [along] and casting forward aquila wood and tusks</l>
<l rend="indent">of hollow-trunked elephants.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
